THE chips are down for Kaizer Chiefs. Their 1-0 loss in the Nedbank Cup final on Saturday had fans heartbroken. But the rest of the country made fun of their loss to underdogs TS Galaxy. It has been four years since Amakhosi has won a trophy. Social media posted numerous memes about the defeat. Most of the fans called for Chiefs football manager Bobby Motaung to step down. They blamed him for the team’s constant losses. ) Qaphela Nozwane? said: “They need to take out Bobby, we will be fine after that.”